   version stable 0.74 0.73
   require MesaLib SDL_net SDL_sound libpng
  optional alsa-lib
  category development/emulator
 attribute x11
    source $SOURCEFORGE_URL dosbox/dosbox/$VERSION/dosbox-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info home  http://dosbox.sourceforge.net/
      info docs  http://www.dosbox.com/wiki/Main_Page
    CFLAGS='-O2'
  CXXFLAGS='-O2'
   LDFLAGS='-Wl,-O1'
      desc 'emulates a 16-bit DOS box or partially implemented 32-bit DOS box
Good for playing sierra graphical adventure games,
and other 16 bit software such as Ultima Underworld.'
